 FRSC  Two persons died yesterday while four others sustained various degrees of injury in a lone accident involving a commercial bus around Fidiwo on the Lagos-Ibadan expressway.  MEANWHILE, two persons escaped death when a truck laden with diesel crashed at Nawfia, along the old Enugu road yesterday. Eyewitnesses said the driver lost control while negotiating a sharp bend. The driver and his conductor came out unhurt.
